{"tid":761570,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集運不要用多寶，員工做事馬虎","createTime":"2018-07-30T13:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T00:15:22.000Z","uid":159206,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f6c2a096bfec48f2df4cda4a448789ce181b9fa8","tid":761570,"uid":159206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:20:48.000Z","msg":"早兩日聯絡多寶網，想份文件改時間取<br />\n當日去自取車取，司機同我講冇呢份文件<br />\n聯絡客戶服務，佢地竟然咁樣回覆我：<br />\n話當日出貨先知唔可以改時間，而同事都無話一定可以改到時間，只係*盡量安排*，要我去貨廠到拎番。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nD員工求求其其，唔可以改間又唔通知我，今日專登請假去拎。如果改唔到，一早搵朋友去拎貨，去到先同我講改唔到，要我去廠拎番件貨，咁堅持呀，件貨大不了味唔要。"},{"pid":"3ac0d2eabb80f2ab5c76350922aa1fa4676140cb","tid":761570,"uid":61967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:29:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早兩日聯絡多寶網，想份文件改時間取<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你漏左講重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地有冇應承實你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f309bcc7fe283d98daf7e1b6cdd9bcde88bb76","tid":761570,"uid":61967,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"你個人麻撚煩，貪平用集運，仲要改嚟改去。同你自己一廂情願以為一定應承實你係兩回事嚟喎"},{"pid":"7adeca67f6463534d50f000f666f14a405db441e","tid":761570,"uid":159206,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"73f309bcc7fe283d98daf7e1b6cdd9bcde88bb76","tid":761570,"uid":61967,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"你個人麻撚煩，貪平用集運，仲要改嚟改去。同你自己一廂情願以為一定應承實你係兩回事嚟喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:00:33.000Z","msg":"我又唔覺得平，平 我就唔要啦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5478d458f71be0fa1f698fda0654bc33baa32cc4","tid":761570,"uid":159206,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3ac0d2eabb80f2ab5c76350922aa